---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-brand-dark text-brand-light pt-20 pb-10 border-t border-white/10 font-sans">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16">
        <!-- Brand Section -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
            <a href="/" class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-white block">
                WHY NOT? <span class="text-brand-accent text-lg italic font-light block -mt-2">perfums</span>
            </a>
            <p class="text-brand-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
                Descubre fragancias que definen tu esencia. Perfumería de autor y marcas de lujo en Santiago de Chile.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Quick Links -->
        <div>
            <h4 class="font-serif text-brand-accent text-lg mb-6 tracking-wide">Explora</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm tracking-widest text-gray-400 uppercase">
                <li><a href="/mujer" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Mujer</a></li>
                <li><a href="/hombre" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Hombre</a></li>
                <li><a href="/unisex" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Unisex</a></li>
                <li><a href="/novedades" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Novedades</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Info -->
        <div>
            <h4 class="font-serif text-brand-accent text-lg mb-6 tracking-wide">Contacto</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-accent shrink-0">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z" />
